<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.10.8">
<l>veñci ṉakkaḷiṟ ṟaiviḷaṅ kāyviḻak kaṉṟu vīciya vīcaṉai pēymakaḷ</l>
<l>tuñca nañcucu vaittuṇṭa tōṉṟalait tōṉṟal vāḷarak kaṉkeṭat tōṉṟiya</l>
<l>nañci ṉaiyamu tattiṉai nātaṉai naccu vārucci mēlniṟkum nampiyai</l>
<l>kañca ṉaittuñca vañcitta vañcaṉaik kaṇṇa maṅkaiyuḷ kaṇṭukoṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I saw for myself in Kaṇṇamaṅkai [the one who is] a fierce, raging elephant,</l>
<l>Īśa who threw a calf so a woodapple fell,</l>
<l rend="indent">the manifestation who ate poison, relishing [it],</l>
<l rend="indent">so the she-demon died,</l>
<l>The poison which appeared so the sword-demon king was ruined,</l>
<l rend="indent">nectar, the lord,</l>
<l>The noble who stands on the heads of those who love [him],</l>
<l rend="indent">the trickster who tricked Kaṁsa so he died.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
